

    
       Last night over at my boss' house, his wife offered to do my laundry so I would have clean clothes to wear today. I was too quick to accept. What happened? Since they didn't really have any clothes for me to change into, I ended up having to wear only a bathrobe the whole night.   We were watching TV, then things took a weird turn. A hot steamy makeout scene. So there I was, sitting there in my bathrobe, next to my boss and his wife, feeling extremely uncomfortable, thinking " Oh man, please let this end, when is this going stop !" Let me tell you I was so glad when that was over. Whew.   Now here's a thought: what would be worse, being with your parents when that happen, or being with your boss and his/her spouse?  
    
    
